    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty\u2014it's basically like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've absolutely babied this car since day one, and it is in flawless condition inside and out. No scratches, no dents, and it still has that fresh car feel. I'm honestly a little sad to see it go, but it\u2019s ready for a new owner who will love it just as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to chat and show it to you!",
      "price": 44500.0,
