    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in showroom condition. This specimen is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system that has been fully overhauled. Power is routed through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a factory M-Variable differential lock. The chassis integrity is absolute, with documented subframe reinforcement and a suspension refresh utilizing OEM bushings to maintain optimal kinematics. Rod bearings have been addressed preventatively, ensuring the reciprocating assembly is bulletproof. Finished in original paint with zero track time, this E46 represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated longitudinal performance. A turn-key acquisition for the collector who demands mechanical perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 12
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint condition. Clean title. No scratches or dents. Interior is spotless. Full service history included. Runs like new.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 12
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offered here is an absolutely pristine 2018 BMW M2, a vehicle that redefines the term 'mint condition.' This enthusiast-owned masterpiece has been housed exclusively in a climate-controlled garage and has never been driven in inclement weather. The Long Beach Blue Metallic exterior is flawless, boasting a deep, glass-like finish thanks to a multi-stage paint correction and professional ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the black Dakota leather seats show zero bolster wear, and the carbon fiber trim is free of any imperfections. Every electronic feature functions perfectly, and the engine bay is clean enough to display. This car comes with a complete, documented service history from BMW-certified technicians, ensuring mechanical perfection. With no stone chips, zero curb rash on the factory alloys, and a spotless undercarriage, this M2 represents a rare opportunity to own a modern classic in showroom state. Included are all original keys, manuals, and a bespoke indoor car cover.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 12
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen of automotive engineering, preserved in impeccable showroom condition. This vehicle has been maintained to an exacting standard, exhibiting a flawless exterior finish and a pristine interior that reflects a history of climate-controlled storage and fastidious care. Every mechanical and aesthetic detail remains in superlative order, offering a driving experience indistinguishable from its original delivery state. This is an investment-grade acquisition for the sophisticated enthusiast who prioritizes unrivaled quality and provenance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
