    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You have got to see this absolute beauty! It\u2019s been my pride and joy, and honestly, it looks and feels just like it did the day it left the showroom. I\u2019ve babied this car since day one\u2014it's always been kept in the garage, and I've made sure it stayed spotless inside and out. It drives like an absolute dream and is just waiting for someone who will love it as much as I have. If you're looking for something that's been cared for with a lot of heart, this is the one! Come take it for a spin! \u2728",
      "price": 43500.0,
